Avtotor Logo Avtotor is an automobile manufacturing company located in Kaliningrad Oblast, Russia. Avtotor was established in 1996, and by 2008 it was one of the largest producers and assemblers of cars in the world. The company’s revenue for 2011 was reported to be approximately 4 billion euros and the company was reported to have 3,500 employees. Source
